Compile btpc.c in Ubuntu and compile btN900.c in scratchbox.

scp btN900 to N900 and run it like below:
	Nokia-N900:~# ./btN900 
	Creating socket...
	success!
	Binding socket...
	success!
	Listen... requested!
	Accepting...
	OK!
	accepted connection from 88:9F:FA:F3:F5:0A 
	received[hello!]

Run btpc in Ubuntu like below:
	$ ./btpc C8:97:9F:E3:28:44
	connectting...
	scuess!
